learning_outcomes.en:
A student who has successfully completed the course:
1) is aware of the major events that took place in the international relations of the Baltic Sea region from the middle of the 16th century until the end of the First World War and of the role played by the Baltics in these events;
2) can associate the wider events taking place in the Baltic sea Region with the developments that were occurring in the Baltics at the same time;
3) has acquired experience in working with sources related to the history of international relations.

learning_outcomes.et:
Kursuse edukalt läbinud üliõpilane:
1)	orienteerub Läänemere regiooni rahvusvahelistes suhetes 16. sajandi keskpaigast kuni Esimese maailmasõja lõpuni 
        aset leidnud olulisemates sündmustes ning rollis, mida Baltikum neis mängis; 
2)	oskab seostada Läänemere regiooni rahvusvahelistes suhetes toimuvat samal ajal Baltikumis aset leidnud arengutega;
3)	on omandanud kogemuse iseseisvaks tööks rahvusvaheliste suhete ajaloo allikatega.
